snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Audio Tapes - She's The True Abuser!
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #amberheard 
Domestic Violence does not only happen to women but, for some reason in our society, it is the woman's voice who is usually heard. 
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, it is known to have had a volatile relationship, and she led people to believe that Johnny was the abuser and she was the victim. But now the truth is finally revealing itself and it is not what a lot of people thought. For those who accused Johnny of being a 'Wife Beater' will have to eat their own words. These revealing audiotapes of Johnny and Amber were posted by the Daily Mail and tell the truth just who the real abuser really was. 
#SupportForJohnnyDepp 

STORY LINK: https://dailym.ai/37cnbxv

Sign Petition to REMOVE AMBER HEARD FROM AQUAMAN: http://chng.it/9cPyj7mFwB
